customListSearch.sortByDescription: Results can be sorted by attributes that are enabled in this library's Lanes & Filters configuration. Selecting "Title" or "Author" will automatically filter out less relevant results.
customListSearch.automaticUpdateDescript: The system will periodically execute this search and automatically update the list with the results.
The search results below represent the titles that would be in the list if it were updated now, but the actual contents of the list will change over time.
customListSearch.manualSelectDescription: The list entries are manually selected.

Move the desired titles from the search results column on the left to the column on the right to add them to the list. Titles may be removed from the list automatically if they become unavailable, but the list is otherwise fixed.
